Package: sfct
Title: Constrained Triangulation for Simple Features
Version: 0.0.1
Authors@R: person("Michael D.","Sumner", role = c("aut", "cre"), email = "mdsumner@gmail.com")
Description: Build constrained Delaunay triangulations from simple features
    objects, applying constraints based on input line segments, and triangle
    properties including maximum area, minimum internal angle.
Depends:
    R (>= 3.3.2)
License: GPL-3
Encoding: UTF-8
LazyData: true
Imports:
    dplyr,
    RTriangle,
    sf
RoxygenNote: 5.0.1
Suggests: testthat,
    covr,
    knitr,
    rmarkdown, 
    viridisLite
VignetteBuilder: knitr
